{"tid":1490791,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一出好戲","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T09:51:38.000Z","uid":274161,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"52eea06900065a0aa874d66ee761c8952ed8bb7b","tid":1490791,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"一出好戲，可惜做過左頭<br />\n<br />\n818大遊行，環時出來讚理性，五毛又轉風向。今日朝早林鄭出來講，只要局勢平靜就開始調查黑警。<br />\n斬人的事，警察到場hea做，唔睇CCTV都可以下午拉到人<br />\n虐待老人更加即刻有回應，高調處理兩個散仔（6月份的事，有無咁橋今日先爆；之前高佬又一直收收埋埋無聲氣）<br />\n<br />\n不言而喻：就係你班勇武特登搞亂局勢，令警察無辦法做事；而家乖乖地咪幾好，政府即刻就回應民意<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位睇路</span></strong>"},{"pid":"780129b50447e4c56063c23719b514df4639e5c4","tid":1490791,"uid":244352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:11:57.000Z","msg":"含撚啦你班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8090cc16eb32ffc708a7274945a6c42d421cab","tid":1490791,"uid":216683,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"傻仔先會咁諗<br />\n6月投訴<br />\n要議員, 搵到真實証據先肯做野同回應<br />\n曝光咗就要做, 無曝光就繼續唔做野,<br />\n係人都知, 俾人發現咗先推兩個散仔CONDOM出黎啦"},{"pid":"5b5da2759e95ef552be7ebe9147bd691774a4334","tid":1490791,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a8aef21694ab2c17fa6a56188eaa6ca277621","tid":1490791,"uid":54109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class